            <p>Teachers and trainers need content that is easy to use and easy to evaluate. The level-quiz model provides both teaching structure and assessment.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <div class="feature-card h-100">
            <div class="feature-icon"><i class="bi bi-bar-chart-line-fill"></i></div>
