            <p>Instead of passive reading, learners complete lessons and quizzes, then track improvements over time through dashboard and profile insights.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-5">What This Application Does</h2>
      <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon"><i class="bi bi-journal-check"></i></div>
            <h5>Structured Learning</h5>
            <p>Organizes civic education into focused levels so you can learn in a clear sequence, from core concepts to applied understanding.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon"><i class="bi bi-ui-checks-grid"></i></div>
