            <p>Each level includes quizzes that help you check understanding, reinforce memory, and identify where more study is needed.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon"><i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow"></i></div>
