            <p>Keeps your score history and progress so you can see strengths, weak areas, and your overall learning growth.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-5">What You Will Learn</h2>
      <p class="text-center text-muted mb-4">The platform covers key civic themes through six progressive levels.</p>
      <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <div class="curriculum-card">
            <div class="curriculum-number">1</div>
            <h5>Constitution and Civic Basics</h5>
            <p>Understand constitutional values, citizenship, rights, and civic responsibilities.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <div class="curriculum-card">
            <div class="curriculum-number">2</div>
            <h5>Public Cleanliness and Waste</h5>
            <p>Learn proper waste management, public hygiene habits, and responsible community practices.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <div class="curriculum-card">
            <div class="curriculum-number">3</div>
            <h5>Traffic and Public Safety</h5>
            <p>Study road safety, basic traffic understanding, and responsible behavior in public spaces.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <div class="curriculum-card">
            <div class="curriculum-number">4</div>
            <h5>Environment and Heritage</h5>
            <p>Build awareness around conservation, sustainability, and respect for natural and cultural heritage.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <div class="curriculum-card">
            <div class="curriculum-number">5</div>
            <h5>Inclusion and Social Harmony</h5>
            <p>Understand diversity, inclusion, and legal and social values that support peaceful coexistence.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <div class="curriculum-card">
            <div class="curriculum-number">6</div>
            <h5>Digital Citizenship</h5>
            <p>Learn safe digital behavior, responsible online participation, and awareness of misinformation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

