    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Walkthrough: From Start to Progress</h2>
      <div class="row text-center g-4">
        <div class="col-md-2">
          <div class="step-card h-100">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <h5>Create Account</h5>
            <p>Register to unlock your personal learning dashboard.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-2">
          <div class="step-card h-100">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <h5>Study a Level</h5>
            <p>Read one lesson at a time in a structured order.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-2">
          <div class="step-card h-100">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <h5>Take the Quiz</h5>
            <p>Attempt the quiz to check your understanding of the lesson.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-2">
          <div class="step-card h-100">
            <div class="step-number">4</div>
            <h5>Get Result</h5>
            <p>See your score and identify what to improve next.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-2">
          <div class="step-card h-100">
            <div class="step-number">5</div>
            <h5>Track Improvement</h5>
            <p>Follow progress trends in dashboard and profile sections.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-2">
          <div class="step-card h-100">
            <div class="step-number">6</div>
            <h5>Continue Learning</h5>
            <p>Move to the next level and keep building civic competence.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
